    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老顽童上了彭大哥的当",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞧清楚了再说。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正想设法查探，只听彭连虎喝道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洞中一人沉着声音道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "梁子翁当年吃过这",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖一怔，问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "彭连虎又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖再问：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "右手仍将他身子提着。彭连虎道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "彭连虎道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "高声叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "转身施展轻功，疾驰而去。一路之上大惑不解：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老顽童，我来啦！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "站直身子，向灵智上人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "灵智上人浑不理会，仍一动不动的坐着。黄蓉伸手往他肩头推去，喝道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伸手探他鼻息，好端端的却在呼吸，一转念间，不由得又好气又好笑，向周伯通道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通圆睁双眼，气鼓鼓的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "转头向弓身躺在地下的灵智上人叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉冷冷的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通一呆，叫声：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "齐声叫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伏魔杖法",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "行有余力",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "举重若轻",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "降龙十八掌",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "连",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大师父！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖一呆，双膝跪地，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柯镇恶仍伸出了手掌，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_zhen_e",
      "speaker_name": "柯镇恶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖哭道：",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柯镇恶听在耳里，怒火愈盛，说道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柯镇恶道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说著作了一揖。周伯通听洪七公如此说，心想我何不也来说上几句，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咦，南帝又犯着你什么了，连他也骂在里头？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通更惊，大叫：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉手指向南，说道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说了话可要作数。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难追",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖大喜，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟子尽力而为，若不告成，死而后已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "颤声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大⋯⋯师⋯⋯师父⋯⋯",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_zhen_e",
      "speaker_name": "柯镇恶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咳，咳！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恶狗拦路",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打狗棒法",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大师父慢走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父，你可知⋯⋯可知为了什么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说到这里，喝了两大口酒，把一只鸡腿都塞入了口里，三咬两嚼，吞入肚中，伸袖一抹口边油腻，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "待听到一灯大师救治黄蓉、锳姑子夜寻仇等事端，只呆呆出神；听到锳姑在青龙滩上忽然发疯，不觉",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父，怎么？你也识得锳姑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父，段皇爷怕他一死之后，没人再制得住欧阳锋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父，我们的事说完了，现下要听你说啦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的事么？嗯，在御厨里我连吃了四次鸳鸯五珍脍，算是过足了瘾，又吃了荔枝白腰子、鹌子羹、羊舌签、姜醋香螺、牡蛎酿羊肚⋯⋯",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么后来老顽童找你不到啦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咦，他们找你干么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "梁子翁他们怎能听老顽童的指派？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洪七公笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洪七公道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父，那日咱们从明霞岛回来⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉微微一笑，道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洪七公奇道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
